this_title: Amy Winehouse: The Day She Came to Dingle
trans_title: 艾米·怀恩豪斯：她来町勾的那天
introduction: Documentary telling the story of the day Amy Winehouse recorded a stunning acoustic performance in a church in the small Irish fishing village of Dingle in 2006.这部纪录片讲述了艾米怀恩豪斯2006年在町勾的小爱尔兰渔村的一个教堂录制一场出色的原声表演那天发生的故事。
chinese_title: 艾米·怀恩豪斯：她来町勾的那天
foreign_title: Amy Winehouse: The Day She Came to Dingle
